Class ContestantInformation

  • java.lang.Object
    • ContestantInformation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable

    public class ContestantInformation
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable
    For this program the user will be applying for a reality show. They will need to answer a skill testing question correctly, and be at least 18 years of age. If they qualify you will get their address and phone number from them to send to the casting director. Date: Friday, October 2, 2015
    Author:
    Rosauro Tuazon
